"https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/the-u-s-murder-rate-is-up-but-still-far-below-its-1980-peak/">它有点真实</a>；事实上，这是特朗普大会演讲的主题。对于 MAGA 人来说，想要重演这部经典老歌是很自然的事情。他们讲述的一个混乱世界的故事（当然要归功于软弱而倒霉的民主党）包括边境安全、乌克兰和加沙的战争，以及最重要的是不断上升的犯罪率。</p><p>但这种说法至少存在一个大问题：美国的<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-18/i-didn-t-think-biden-affected-crime-rates-i-was-wrong?sref=R8NfLgwS">犯罪率正在迅速下降</a>。</p><p>当一个人<a href="https://x.com/Noahpinion/status/1787898590087815481">敢于在社交媒体上说出这一真相</a>时，人们通常会被愤怒的 MAGA 类型所淹没，他们否认犯罪率正在下降。以下只是这些回复的一小部分： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3bf00b5-4af9-420c-aa6e-4576bd1efffa_924x485.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3bf00b5-4af9-420c-aa6e-4576bd1efffa_924x485.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3bf00b5-4af9-420c-aa6e-4576bd1efffa_924x485.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3bf00b5-4af9-420c-aa6e-4576bd1efffa_924x485.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3bf00b5-4af9-420c-aa6e-4576bd1efffa_924x485.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2