iv></div></figure></div><p>过去几年的一个不幸的教训是，如果美国人不想相信一个简单明了的事实，他们就不会相信。无论有多少数据、仔细的研究或合理的论证都无法说服他们。因此，很多美国人将在 11 月份前往投票站，他们绝对、 <a href="https://abcnews.go.com/US/us-stats-show-violent-crime-dramatically-falling-rising/story?id=108042096">完全相信</a>拜登领导下的犯罪率飙升。</p><p>很多……但也许不是全部。我固执地相信，仍然有很大一部分美国人<em>会对</em>证据做出反应，所以我所能做的就是提供这些证据并希望有人关心。</p><p>那么我们来看看数据吧。首先，我们来谈谈FBI的估计。联邦调查局有一个名为<a href="https://cde.ucr.cjis.gov/LATEST/webapp/#/pages/home">“统一犯罪报告”</a>的数据集，他们试图根据警方向他们报告的内容来估计美国的犯罪数量。该数据显示，2023 年犯罪率全面下降，并在 2024 年初加速下降： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg" width="834" height="499" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:499,&quot;width&quot;:834,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:105085,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4249b208-1420-418c-9a2f-d60afc442359_834x499.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-18/i-didn-t-think-biden-affected-crime-rates-i-was-wrong?sref=R8NfLgwS">贾斯汀·福克斯</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在，只要你提供这些数据，一群 MAGA 人士就会跳出来<a href="https://x.com/DefiyantlyFree/status/1802825808110608791">声称 FBI 数据是假的</a>。这些说法要么是严重误解，要么是对<a href="https://www.themarshallproject.org/2022/08/15/see-if-police-in-your-state-reported-crime-data-to-the-fbi?utm_source=The+Trace+mailing+list&amp;utm_campaign=b246e29f22-trace_bulletin_aug_07_2023&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_term=0_-b246e29f22-%5BLIST_EMAIL_ID%5D">2021 年发生的真实事件</a>的故意歪曲。 2021 年，联邦调查局 (FBI) 更改了城市警察部门报告犯罪的系统。新系统很难使用，因此那一年几乎有三分之一的警察部门没有发送电话号码。</p><p>一些人显然认为这意味着联邦调查局只是假设犯罪数量下降，因为向他们报告的犯罪数量减少了。事实并非如此。联邦调查局试图根据报告城市的数据来<em>估计</em>未报告城市发生的犯罪数量。他们显示的总数包括对未报告犯罪的估计。</p><p>现在，这些估计可能会被打破！如果犯罪增加最多的城市也是那些没有报告的城市，那么联邦调查局很容易会错过这一点，并且其估计可能会太低。但联邦调查局<strong>并不是</strong>简单地统计警察部门向其报告的所有犯罪行为。他们并不是简单地说“哎呀，告诉我们他们的犯罪数字的城市越来越少，所以我猜美国发生的犯罪也越来越少！”。 FBI 没那么蠢，他们也不认为<em>你</em>那么蠢。</p><p>但无论如何，这一切都有点跑题了，因为到了 2022 年，报告问题已经基本得到解决。 Jeff Asher 是一位以研究这些数据为生的著名犯罪学家，他发表了<a href="https://jasher.substack.com/p/is-the-nibrs-transition-to-blame">一篇很好的文章，解释了</a>到 2022 年警察部门如何再次开始报告：</p><blockquote><p>当各机构未能报告时，联邦调查局会估算犯罪数量，以填补估算全国数字时的空白。当只有 5% 左右的犯罪数据时，这通常不是什么大问题，但如果您估计 35%，那就是一个大问题。这引发了……关于 2021 年国家犯罪数据的大量问题。如果您可以看到图片的 90% 或 95%，那么您可以比仅看到图片的 65% 更准确地猜测该图片是什么。</p><p>幸运的是，FBI 在 2022 年做出了改变，允许非 NIBRS 机构提交数据，覆盖率在 2022 年大幅提高至 94% 左右——这一水平与历史报告标准相当……[M]超过 85% 的美国人口到 2023 年底由 NIBRS 报告机构覆盖（包括该国 10 个最大城市中的 9 个）。加入非 NIBRS 机构应该意味着 2023 年数据再次正常覆盖。</p></blockquote><p>这是他的关键图： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg" width="921" height="520" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:520,&quot;width&quot;:921,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:54795,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8c089fa-7fb8-410f-99a6-f4af91bb7055_921x520.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>所以2022年以后的FBI数据应该还不错。</p><p>但如果只有<em>这一数据来源</em>告诉我们犯罪率正在下降，我仍然会告诉你要保持怀疑。在<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-many-of-our-facts-about-society">很多情况</a>下，即使是最仔细收集的数据后来也会出现大问题，从而改变我们对事实的整体理解。如果只有联邦调查局报告犯罪率下降，那么几年后，一些细心的数据侦探可能会发现一些错误，表明“让美国再次伟大”的人毕竟是对的，在拜登的领导下，犯罪率确实飙升。</p><p>但幸运的是，我们实际上拥有<em>大量</em>有关犯罪的数据源，尤其是有关谋杀和其他暴力犯罪的数据源。尽管对于过去两年半犯罪率下降了<em>多少</em>存在轻微分歧，但人们对趋势的方向达成了广泛共识。</p><p>首先，Jeff Asher 拥有<a href="https://www.ahdatalytics.com/dashboards/ytd-murder-comparison/">自己的犯罪数据</a>，由他的公司 AH Datalytics 收集。 AH Datalytics 通过致电警察部门并询问他们的犯罪号码来获取这些数据。它显示 2023 年和 2024 年初的谋杀案急剧下降，低于 2016-2019 年的水平。以下是贾斯汀·福克斯 (Justin Fox) 绘制的图表，将 FBI 到 2022 年的数据与 Asher 2023 年和 2024 年初的数据结合起来： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg" width="708" height="429.1975155279503" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c8143310-65eb-453e-ba0d-b9696a6c798b_805x488.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:488,&quot;width&quot;:805,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:708,&quot;bytes&quot;:128978,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%