o:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6ef8884c-d19f-4a64-83d3-4306eb4c9e6d_680x616.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.ft.com/content/22089f01-8468-4905-8e36-fd35d2b2293e">ft</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>保罗·克鲁格曼（Paul Krugman）声称，这只是一种统计幻觉，这是由于欧元以来欧元以来欧元以来的衰弱引起的： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg" width="632" height="723.394270122783" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:839,&quot;width&quot;:733,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:632,&quot;bytes&quot;:115320,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1b8d0ceb-656f-445e-abd9-c2030a0efd27_733x839.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但是，构建FT图表的方式，您不需要应用PPP调整。如果您以100的价格启动我们和欧元区GDP，则可以使用每个区域的价格来计算随着时间的推移实际增长。因此，《金融时报》图中的增长线应该已经反映了两个区域之间的价格差异 - 换句话说，它们原则上<em>已经针对PPP进行了调整</em>。</p><p>那么为什么大差异呢？<a href="https://x.com/ThomasPHI2/status/1803176004988313736">托马斯·菲利普（Thomas Philippon）意识到</a>，美国和欧元区通货膨胀率与计算PPP的世界银行人数计算的价格数字<em>大不相同</em>。两种不同的研究人员发现了非常不同的价格数字 - 欧元区人们认为他们的价格上涨了比世界银行人民想象的要高得多。</p><p>而且还不清楚谁是对的。人们正在研究差异，但是现在我们只是不知道欧洲是否主要与美国保持同步或落后。</p><p>认识不确定性的情况如何？</p><p>无论如何，当我找到这些谜团的答案时，我会告诉您。同时，这里的最大收获是，各国必须根据偶尔有巨大问题的数据做出改变世界的决策。这就是我们不确定世界的本质。我们唯一能做的就是尽可能多地查看尽可能多的高质量，经过仔细研究的数据源，并试图找出任何分歧的原因。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-84f?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-84f?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p></p>; 
Give us your ideas on how to deal with Chinese chips!A policy competition from the Federation of American Scientists, Chris Miller, ChinaTalk, and me https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/give-us-your-ideas-on-how-to-deal https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/give-us-your-ideas-on-how-to-dealNoah Smith Fri, 21 Jun 2024 04:23:02 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg" width="704" height="528" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:921,&quot;width&quot;:1228,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:704,&quot;bytes&quot;:264282,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ef2b8c5-3fd6-4294-8acb-4878ecad8ec4_1228x921.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>今天我有一些特别的东西。我不会告诉你我的想法，而是要你的！</p><p>一年前，<a href="https://fas.org/">美国科学家联合会</a>与马特·伊格利亚斯（Matt Yglesias）合作，以众包人民对<a href="https://www.slowboring.com/p/your-best-ideas-on-increasing-housing">增加住房供应的政策</a>的想法。他们得到了一些非常聪明且有趣的建议，因此他们决定进行更多此类比赛。</p><p>在<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSekYm0Vtj7rPnf9-rpuiP2GgqTkjfAxo5a3eBK0415B3I44Gw/viewform">第二场比赛</a>中，我和FAS与出色的书籍<em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Chip-War-Worlds-Critical-Technology/dp/1982172002">Chip War</a></em>的作者<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/interview-chris-miller-historian">Chris Miller</a>和经营出色的博客<a href="https://www.chinatalk.media/">Ch​​inatalk</a>的Jordan Schneider合作。因为这场比赛就是如何处理中国计算机芯片。</p><p>美国已经实施了<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/biden-declares-economic-war-on-the">出口控制</a>，以阻止中国在先进的尖端筹码中获得技术优势。但是，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/three-holes-in-the-us-economic-strategy">正如我在最近的一篇文章中所解释的那样</a>，出口控制措施没有希望阻止中国建造更简单的芯片类型（称为“传统芯片”，“基本芯片”或“ Tagring-Edge-Edge Chips”）。这些传统筹码用于我们经济中的大量事情，从汽车到智能手机再到战斗机。</p><p>而且中国正在准备以绝对惊人的数字来建造这些旧筹码。查看加利福尼亚大学全球冲突与合作研究所的<a href="https://ucigcc.org/blog/chinas-evolving-semiconductor-strategy/">吉米·古德里奇（Jimmy Goodrich）的这篇文章</a>，以及 <a href="https://rhg.com/research/thin-ice-us-pathways-to-regulating-china-sourced-legacy-chips/">《辉煌集团》（Rhodium Group）的这篇帖子</a>。基本上，中国正在对其成功应用于电池和电动汽车的传统芯片采用相同的方法，包括大量规模和巨大的补贴。已经，</p><p>这基本上给美国带来了至少三个潜在的危险：</p><ol><li><p>首先，中国可以通过在传统芯片市场中占领非中国芯片制造商的大量收入，从而使他们更难维持其领先的芯片业务。<a href="https://www.theregister.com/2024/05/29/elliott_letter_texas_instruments/">投资者已经向美国公司施加压力</a>，要求避免通过取消其半导体工厂与中国竞争。</p></li><li><p>其次，如果中国控制着传统筹码市场，它可能会切断我们在战争中的筹码。</p></li><li><p>第三，中国安全服务可能能够将门倒入中国制造的筹码中，使用它们来监视甚至攻击美国基础设施。</p></li></ol><p>换句话说，有很多国家安全原因可以将中国制造的旧筹码置于我们的供应链之外。但是我们该怎么做呢？这是一个棘手的问题。</p><p>首先，正如事物的那样，<em>我们甚至都不知道</em>哪种产品包含中国制造的芯片。如果越南制造的手机或墨西哥制造的PC包括中国制造的旧版筹码，那么美国目前无法了解。</p><p>其次，即使我们<em>知道</em>，禁止这些筹码在政治上可能不受欢迎。许多美国公司希望尽可能便宜地获取芯片，尤其是对于新的AI应用程序。我们需要某种方法来使筹码限制在政治上可口。</p><p>最后，许多中国遗产筹码以及包含它们的产品 - 不会在美国或我们的盟国出售。我们如何确保非中国芯片制造商在越南，巴西，印度尼西亚等市场中保持竞争力？</p><p>因此，我们向您寻求帮助。我们希望您对如何处理中国不断上升的旧芯片行业的想法。这是竞争的详细信息，以及有关如何<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSekYm0Vtj7rPnf9-rpuiP2GgqTkjfAxo5a3eBK0415B3I44Gw/viewform">提交想法的</a>说明：</p><h3>比赛的细节</h3><p>美国应该采取什么步骤（如果有的话）来解决中国日益增长的传统芯片制造业份额？</p><p> <em>Chip War</em>的美国科学家联合会，Noahpinion，Chinatalk和Chris Miller兴奋地发起了一项政策提案竞赛，以提出有关美国政府应如何应对的巧妙想法。</p><p>要探索的关键角度：</p><ul><li><p><strong>定义问题</strong>：中国遗产筹码行业的哪些危险是美国应认真对待的危险？</p></li><li><p><strong>优先考虑补救措施</strong>：在供求方面，哪种潜在行动的混合方式最有效地解决了所确定的问题？</p></li></ul><p>强有力的提交应<strong>至少运行2000个单词</strong>。有关写作结构的一些灵感，请参阅<a href="https://fas.org/day-one-project/">第1天项目</a>的备忘录。</p><p>要提交您的想法，<strong>请在7月15日之前<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSekYm0Vtj7rPnf9-rpuiP2GgqTkjfAxo5a3eBK0415B3I44Gw/viewform?usp=send_form">填写此在线表格</a></strong>。最佳提交的作者将获得500美元和在Chinatalk进行采访。获胜者和亚军都将在Noahpinion上获得文章。我们可能还会要求一个或多个人将您的想法推向DC的人们！</p><p><strong>进一步阅读</strong></p><p>要查看人们已经在想什么，请查看Rhodium Group <a href="https://rhg.com/research/thin-ice-us-pathways-to-regulating-china-sourced-legacy-chips/">关于该主题的最新报告</a>，该报告提供了更多的市场环境，并介绍了美国政府可以部署的潜在政策工具菜单 - 尽管建议可能包括其他提案。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png" width="1456" height="1276" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/bfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1276,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfed70eb-f017-4cc9-9d59-d4a7c0f7a279_1600x1402.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 2