China's demographics will be fine through mid-centuryThere is no imminent crisis. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/chinas-demographics-will-be-fine https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/chinas-demographics-will-be-fineNoah Smith Thu, 20 Jun 2024 05:05:21 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg" width="913" height="535" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:535,&quot;width&quot;:913,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:96162,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c98f863-a108-4f15-9359-669b8b49c003_913x535.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">图片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@lanlinn?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Lin Lin</a> <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/a-group-of-people-walking-through-a-field-of-flowers-NuW6GdllbU8?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">摄</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>在关于中国经济的讨论中，人口统计问题的问题很多。 2022年，中国的人口 <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/01/18/china/china-population-drop-explainer-intl-hnk/index.html">开始减少</a>（巧合的是，印度的人口<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/china-reacts-india-overtake-worlds-most-populous-country-economy-rcna80581">超过了中国</a>）。该国的生育率几十年前已经降至替代水平以下， <a href="https://www.wsj.com/world/china/chinas-fertility-rate-dropped-sharply-study-shows-e97e647f">最近再次下降至1.09</a> ，这是世界上最低的率之一，甚至低于日本。</p><p>这促使人们对中国经济的未来以及来自中国内部的人们和外国观察员的未来进行了巨大的努力。例如， <a href="https://www.wsj.com/world/china/chinas-fertility-rate-dropped-sharply-study-shows-e97e647f">这是WSJ中的报价</a>：</p><blockquote><p> “随着人口达到顶峰，中国将显示出日本化的迹象，”国家支持的智囊团国家金融与发展研究所副主任Yin Jianfeng在6月发表的一篇文章中写道。元敦促中国政府在抚养儿童和教育上花更多的钱，以避免日本的命运，而日本经历了数十年的停滞。</p></blockquote><p>这是<a href="https://www.economist.com/china/2024/04/09/chinas-high-stakes-struggle-to-defy-demographic-disaster">经济学家</a>：</p><blockquote><p>结果，中国的经济也有可能在减少。政府带来了巨大的照顾负担，感觉到了一场即将来临的灾难……中国正在变老之前。 2008年，当日本人口开始下降时，其每人的GDP已经以今天的美元约为47,500美元。中国只有21,000美元。由于更多的钱用于保护老化的公民，因此少于工厂可以消费或投资。</p></blockquote><p>从<a href="https://theconversation.com/chinas-doom-loop-a-dramatically-smaller-and-older-population-could-create-a-devastating-global-slowdown-221554">谈话</a>中，这是我能找到的最可怕的帖子：</p><blockquote><p>人口转移会导致<a href="https://www.investopedia.com/doom-loop-6748009">“厄运循环”</a> ……随着降低的生产率开始影响特定领域的生产，中国可能被迫增加进口量以满足这些行业的需求……这可能会严重影响创新和企业家精神，从而进一步降低生产率。<a href="https://www.nber.org/system/files/working_papers/w26651/w26651.pdf">新想法</a>……推动经济增长。劳动力的规模会影响创新，因为随着受雇个人的数量萎缩，新想法的库变得更狭窄……如果人口增长变成<a href="https://www.nber.org/system/files/working_papers/w26651/w26651.pdf">负面或降至零</a>，那么这些思想背后的知识停滞不前。此外，有证据表明，一个人的创新活动和科学产出的<a href="https://www.cato.org/cato-journal/spring/summer-2018/demographics-their-implications-economy-policy#demographic-implications-for-economic-growth">顶峰</a>约为30至40岁……因此，当前的人口趋势可能会扼杀中国的技术进步和创新……同时，研究表明， <a href="https://www.econbiz.de/Record/entrepreneurship-and-demographics-liang-james/10013112441">研究</a>表明由于年轻人的百分比与企业家活动呈正相关，企业家精神可能会受到人口老龄化的负面影响。这妨碍了经济的活力，并有助于经济增长缓慢。</p></blockquote><p>现在，我绝对<em>认为</em><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/chinese-demography">这是中国长期的问题</a>。实际上，在这方面，中国远非独特 - 每个发达国家都在迅速衰老，而且大多数发展中国家都不远。</p><p>而且确实<em>会对</em>人口衰老产生负面影响。我在这篇文章中写了有关这些问题的文章： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;f6b7772c-4077-458e-93c0-4fd566508326&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;The problem with population growth projections is that they naturally follow an exponential curve. When &#8220;like begets like&#8221; &#8212; when the number of kids is just proportional to how many people are currently alive to have kids &#8212; you get a function that either explodes to infinity or decays to zero as time goes on. So no matter what the fertility rate is, humanity is&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Humanity is going to shrink&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-08-22T21:43:59.679Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F832a104e-51e3-4585-8548-b5659024107e_919x690.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/humanity-is-going-to-shrink&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:136311679,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:263,&quot;comment_count&quot;:201,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p>实际上，人口的收缩实际上不是问题 - 而是<em>老化</em>。老年依赖比率上升的确给劳动者带来了巨大的经济负担，而老龄化的劳动力可能确实会降低创新和生产力的增长。尽管是自动化的，但这是正确的。一个拥有老年人的世界最重的世界将是一个年轻人在全球范围内越来越努力地辛苦劳作的世界。</p><p>但是在短期内，我认为对中国人口统计学的灾难性造成的灾难性。拼命搜寻以驳斥中国竞争威胁的理由的美国人可能会诱使抓住该国的低生育能力。但是中国的经济可能性不会“ po”，而是从人口衰老中消失。实际上，正如我要解释的那样，直到本世纪下半叶，它可能不会遇到重大问题。</p><p>同时，中国领导人对该国的人口统计的恐慌并做一些非常轻率的事情存在更大的危险。我的前彭博同事哈尔品牌（Hal Brands） <a href="https://democracyparadox.com/2023/07/11/hal-brands-thinks-china-is-a-declining-power-heres-why-thats-a-problem/">辩称</a>，由于担心如果等待了，中国可能会在未来几年内在亚洲发动战争，它的力量将会下降 - 类似于德国在1914年急于战争，因为它的领导人相信他们的领导人相信他们的领导窗户正在消失。正如我将显示的那样，这种担忧是没有根据的。但这并不是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/what-if-xi-jinping-isnt-that-competent">习近平造成的第一个皮疹错误</a>。</p><p>因此，了解美国人和中国人民都可以理解中国人口状况的非愤怒。</p><h4>中国在管道中有一个婴儿凸起</h4><p>中国人口统计学的第一个也是最重要的原因是，他们拥有的是目前5至15岁的年轻人，这将减轻未来几年的人口压力。</p><p>维基百科（Wikipedia）为中国拥有良好的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aging_of_China#/media/File:China_population_pyramid_from_2023_to_2100.gif">动画人口金字塔</a>，并从非预测中获取了数据。这是2024年金字塔的样子。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg" width="690" height="565.9642857142857" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:689,&quot;width&quot;:840,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:690,&quot;bytes&quot;:137350,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc924e6d0-5bdf-4ea7-b80e-b823af2b6d42_840x689.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">根据Tweedle改编 -<a href="http://CC BY-SA 4.0, https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=127018432">自己的工作</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>如您所见，中国目前的年轻劳动一代（Zoomers）是一代人。但是，比这更年轻的一代人 - 目前5至15岁的Alpha是比变焦者更大的一代。</p><p>从经典意义上讲，中国的alpha并不是真正的“婴儿繁荣”，而5至15年前的生育率没有增加。取而代之的是，alpha是大型千禧一代的<em>人群回响</em>，它本身就是中国极大的婴儿繁荣一代的回声。美国在婴儿繁荣期间的生育率为3.5。 <a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/fertility-rate-with-projections?time=earliest..2021&amp;country=~CHN">中国超过6岁</a>。中国之所以拥有很大的alpha，是因为当时它确实有很多潮一流的潮流。</p><p>无论如何，随着接下来十年中的工作年龄，他们将稳定中国的人口统计信息。在开始缓慢下降之前，中国的工作年龄人口实际上预计将在未来几年内<em>增加</em>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6ae66d-9423-47be-acc0-07030f519286_1020x812.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6ae66d-9423-47be-acc0-07030f519286_1020x812.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6ae66d-9423-47be-acc0-07030f519286_1020x812.jpeg 848w, https://substa